location.fullValue: Updated, Well-Maintained 4br Home On 2 Acre Corner Lot In Popular Ivy Neighborhood

data.description: ***Unique Opportunity for an ASSUMABLE LOAN at 3.25% interest rate***  Brand New home, completed in 2022, this home offers an OPEN FLOOR PLAN with vaulted ceilings, 1st floor primary bedroom suite, charming-cottage-style finishes throughout and a walk-out basement with office & full bath. The classic Kitchen includes the on-trend look--white upper cabinets and dark grey lower cabinetry, stainless appliances & granite counters. Many extras, including-crown molding in kitchen/living/dining room, hardiplank/stone exterior, spacious front porch, asphalt driveway, gas fireplace with slate surround. Quality 2 X6 construction in this new build. This home is located in a quiet cul de sac community and backs to serene natural wooded views with mountain views from the front porch. Firefly Fiber Optic Internet is reported to be installed Winter of 2023.
